      </h6><ul><li class="nav-item"><a href="//nation.foxnews.com">Fox Nation</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="//shop.foxnews.com">Fox News Shop</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/go">Fox News Go</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="//radio.foxnews.com/">Fox News Radio</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="//insider.foxnews.com">Fox News Insider</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/alerts/subscribe">Newsletters</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/newsletter-signup/alerts">Alerts</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="//radio.foxnews.com/podcast">Podcasts</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/apps-products">Apps &amp; Products</a></li></ul></nav></div></div><div class="header-lower"><div><div class="branding"><a href="//www.foxnews.com" class="logo">Fox News</a></div><div class="legal"><ul><li><a href="/terms-of-use">Terms of Use</a></li><li><a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a></li><li><a href="/closed-captioning">Closed Captioning Policy</a></li><li><a href="//help.foxnews.com">Help</a></li></ul><p class="copyright">
